text: Eerikki is a Finnish masculine given name. It is a cognate of the name Eric.Nordic Names Eerikki. Retrieved 9 July 2019 Individuals bearing the name Eerikki include; *Eerikki Koivu (born 1979), ice hockey player *Eerikki Tuurenpoika (fl. 15th-century; also known as Eric Bielke and Eric Tureson), royal councillor of Sweden, knight and feudal fiefholder *Eerikki Viljanen (born 1975), politician ==References== Category:Masculine given names Category:Finnish masculine given names
title: Eerikki
